column5: *Dynamic Inventory* - INQUIRE FIRST-  *There maybe a cleaning fee of $88 if the booking request is for 3 days or less.*  One Bedroom: King in master, sleeper sofa in living area. Maximum occupancy is 4.  High season rates are: Weekend : $250 Weekday : $200  The current rate on the calendar will be valid if the booking request is within 5 days of arrival.
